          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "基础设置（必填）：\nlauncher_root 填写 LTX Desktop 的 run.bat 所在路径，例如：\nD:/LTX2.3-1.0.4\n也可以先留空，手动启动桌面端\n\nauto_start 打开才能自动运行桌面端\n\n简单理解（不需修改）：\n\nhealth_timeout_s = 等桌面端启动/连通的耐心值\nrequest_timeout_s = 等一次生成任务完成的耐心值\n它们不会改变画质、显存策略或生成效果，只控制“等多久才算超时”。\n\nPublic example:\nLeave `launcher_root` empty if you start LTX Desktop manually.\nEnable `auto_start` only when you want ComfyUI to launch it for you."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        856.9720086777879,
        264.6600383014368
      ],
      "size": [
        315.4534871170986,
        171.73985817897096
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 5,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {
        "ue_properties": {
          "widget_ue_connectable": {},
          "version": "7.8",
          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "可用最高显存上限 (GB, 0为全开优先显存)\n0 = 全开、偏性能\n正数 = 限额、偏省显存\n\napply_now：意思是“现在立刻下发到桌面端生效”。你想马上改当前运行环境，就开 true\n\nlow_vram_mode：开启低显存模式以最低显存运行，直接覆盖上面显存输入的限制参数。\n\nVRAM note:\n`vram_limit_gb = 0` means unlimited prefetch.\n`low_vram_mode = true` takes priority over the numeric limit."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
